  "website": "https://www.yealink.com",
  "description": "Yealink Network Technology Co., Ltd., together with its subsidiaries, provides video conferencing, voice communications, and collaboration solutions in Europe, the Americas, and internationally. The company offers Microsoft and Zoom device products comprising Teams rooms systems, Zoom rooms systems, USB cameras and BYOD kits, space IOT devices, room audio devices, room system accessories, room mount kits and cables, teams phones, and zoom phones; headset products consisting of Bluetooth and DECT wireless headsets, wired headsets, speakerphones, headset accessories, and headset selectors; IP phone products, such as team phones, zoom phones, conference phones, DECT phones, Wi-Fi IP phones, 4G phones, and phone accessories; management platforms comprising device management platforms, management cloud services, and USB connect management services; and EoS and EoL products. It also provides finance, education, healthcare, and manufacturing solutions; future workers, headset and handset, personal collaboration, and desktop video solutions; Microsoft Teams room and phone, AV ONE, SkySound audio, and BYOD solutions; small, medium, large, and extra-large room solutions; Zoom rooms, phone, and meetings solutions; RingCentral, 3CX, Extron, Broadsoft, Metaswitch, and BlueJeans solutions; and home support, pre-sale, after-sale, and Yealink Academy services. In addition, the company engages in software development and information system integration services; technology promotion and application services; and the sale of unified communication terminals. Yealink Network Technology Co., Ltd. was incorporated in 2001 and is based in Xiamen, China.",
